    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for all my commutes and weekend trips. The ride is smooth, the interior is clean, and it\u2019s definitely ready for its next adventure with a new owner! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
