    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and reliability. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish, showing only the lightest signs of road use, while the alloy wheels remain crisp and curbing-free. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is well-preserved, and every feature\u2014from the responsive touchscreen interface to the panoramic sunroof\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and a recent multi-point inspection. The engine pulls strongly and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a confident driving experience. Complete with a full service history and two sets of keys, this car is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
