    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. This beauty has been a total joy to own and is still in really solid shape! It's been well-loved and runs like a charm, making it the perfect reliable ride for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and I\u2019ve always made sure to keep up with it. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale so someone else can start enjoying it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 28900.0,
