    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L inline-six breathes through individual throttle bodies and pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to preserve chassis torque-load integrity. The suspension features upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust and the limited-slip differential provides exceptional exit traction. A purist\u2019s spec focused on performance over concours display.",
